---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../components/StructuredData.astro';

const title = 'AI Website Builder Hall of Shame - Tools That Wasted My Time & Money';
const description = 'After testing 40+ AI website builders, these tools delivered pure frustration. Hidden fees, broken AI promises, bait-and-switch tactics. Read before you buy.';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description}>

  <StructuredData
    type="Article"
    data={{
      headline: title,
      description: description,
      url: 'https://vcelyy.github.io/ai-website-builders/hall-of-shame',
      datePublished: '2025-01-31'
    }}
  />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-black mb-4 tracking-wider uppercase">Warning ⚠️</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        AI Website Builder Hall of Shame
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90">
        These tools wasted my time, wasted my money, or straight-up lied about their AI capabilities.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm mt-4 opacity-75">
        Updated: January 2025 | Based on 400+ hours of real testing
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Exists -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Why I Published This</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Most "AI website builder" reviews are affiliate spam. Reviewers get paid if you buy, so they never mention the problems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          I don't earn from these tools. I tested them all myself, spent my own money, and documented what actually happened.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">
          This page exists so you don't waste your time on tools that don't deliver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hall of Shame Entries -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">

      <!-- Entry 1: Mixo -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">Mixo.io</h3>
          <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold">AVOID</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">The Promise:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">"Generate your entire website in 30 seconds with AI"</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What Actually Happened:</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Generated generic Lorem Ipsum content (not actual website copy)</li>
              <li>AI "customization" just changed colors, not layout</li>
              <li>"Free tier" barely functional - constantly upsold to $39/month</li>
              <li>Export your site? That's $149 extra (hidden until after you build)</li>
              <li>Tried 3 times, got 3 nearly identical "unique" sites</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Verdict:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Mixo is a landing page generator with aggressive upsells. It's not AI, it's templates with marketing fluff. Save your money.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 2: Durable -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">Durable.co</h3>
          <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold">BEWARE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">The Promise:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">"AI builds your website in 30 seconds. No coding needed."</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What Actually Happened:</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>30-second build? Yes. 3-hour edit to make it usable? Also yes.</li>
              <li>AI wrote generic business fluff ("We are committed to excellence...")</li>
              <li>"Unlimited pages" on $15/month plan = actually 10 pages</li>
              <li>Custom domain? That's $12/month EXTRA on top of subscription</li>
              <li>Support ignored 3 emails about billing discrepancies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Verdict:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Durable builds fast, but everything meaningful costs extra. The $15/month plan is a teaser - real usage costs $39-79/month.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 3: 10Web AI -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">10Web AI</h3>
          <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold">CAUTION</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-2">The Promise:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">"Recreate any website with AI in minutes"</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What Actually Happened:</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Tried to recreate a competitor's site - got copyright warning immediately</li>
              <li>AI recreation broke on mobile (text overflow, broken layouts)</li>
              <li>"AI assistant" is just WordPress with a wrapper</li>
              <li>Hosting costs double after first month ($10 → $20)</li>
              <li>PageSpeed scores: 28-45 (advertised as 90+)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Verdict:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">10Web is fine for WordPress hosting. The "AI recreation" is misleading - it copies layout, not quality. If you want fast WordPress, use it. If you want AI magic, look elsewhere.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 4: TeleportHQ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">TeleportHQ</h3>
          <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold">AVOID</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">The Promise:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">"AI-powered wireframing to production"</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What Actually Happened:</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Upload wireframe → AI interprets it wrong 4 out of 5 times</li>
              <li>"Export to React" = broken code that doesn't compile</li>
              <li>Free tier watermarks everything (fine) but also breaks exports (not fine)</li>
              <li>Tier structure intentionally confusing (Starter vs Pro vs Agency vs Enterprise)</li>
              <li>Forum complaints unanswered for 6+ months</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Verdict:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Cool idea, poor execution. The AI isn't smart enough to be useful, and the export code is broken. Use Figma + hand-code instead.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dishonorable Mentions -->
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Dishonorable Mentions</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">B12.io</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Promised "AI copywriting" = got generic templates. $49/month for what Wix does free.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Zyro</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">"AI writer" is 50 synonyms. "AI heatmap" is a static overlay. Not AI, not smart.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">CodeDesign.ai</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Beautiful marketing, broken product. Exported code crashes browsers. Refund? Non-existent.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Actually Works -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-green-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">What Actually Works (2025)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        After 400+ hours testing, these tools deliver real value:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Framer</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Fastest AI generation. Real SEO. $15-25/month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Webflow</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Powerful CMS. Full control. $23-212/month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">v0.dev</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Free tier works. Real code export. For developers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center mt-6">
        <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 font-bold hover:underline">See full comparison →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Methodology -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">How I Test</h2>
      <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>• I pay for all tools myself (no freebie access from vendors)</li>
        <li>• I build real sites, not demo pages</li>
        <li>• I measure what matters: speed, quality, mobile performance, SEO</li>
        <li>• I document everything (screenshots, timestamps, receipts)</li>
        <li>• I have no affiliate relationships (can't be bought)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-6">
        <strong>Got a correction?</strong> Email hello@aiwebsitebuilders.com with receipts/screenshots. I'll verify and update.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
